## Additional Notes
- There is still a warning about insightface not being installed automatically for 
  the Legacy Preprocessor. This is expected and users are instructed to manually 
  install it if needed: `pip install insightface`
- The opencv-contrib-python package has a dependency warning about numpy version, 
  but this doesn't affect functionality

